: null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "A blow of Ali on the day of khandaq is better than the worship of Jinns and men.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Roz'e Khandaq, Ali ki ek zarbat tamaam Jinn o Ins ki ibaadat se Afzal hai.", "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ZARBA-TUN A’LIYYIN YAW-MAL KHANDA-QE KHAI-ROOM MIN I’BAADA-TIS SAQLAINE.", "ArabicText1": "ضَرْبَۃُ عَلِیٍّ یَوْمَ الْخَنْدَقِ خَیْرٌ مِّنْ عِبَادَۃِ الثَّقَلَیْنِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013106, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Upon entering the Mosque one should perform 2 rakats namaz of respect, then recite Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s). Recite the <Ziyarat Jame’a Kabir> and then recite this dua…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Masjid mein daakhil hone par 2 rakat namaz, ehteraame masjid ki niyyat se adaa kare. Phir Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) ke baad <ziyarat Jame’a Kabir> aur phir is tarah kahe…", "UrduDescription": "اس مسجد میں جاکر ۲ رکعت نماز تحیت مسجد پڑھے اور تسبیح فاطمہ ؑ کے بعد <زیارتِ جامعہ کبیرہ> پڑھے اور پھر یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013107, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O succor of the distressed! O fulfiller of the prayers of the distressed! Save me from my grief, agony and sadness just as You saved Your Prophet from his grief, agony and sadness, and You were sufficient for him against the terrors of his enemies in this place.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay dukhi logo’n ki faryaad ko pohonch ne waale, ay be-qaraaro’n ki dua qabool karne waale, ay gham ke maaro’n ki madad karne waale, meri sakhti, tangi, pareshaani, takleef aur ranj o gham dur kar de jaisa keh Tu ne apne nabi ki pareshaani dur farmaayi aur dushman se khouf mein unka madad-gaar huwa, duniya o aakherat ki pareshaaniyo’n mein meri kifaayat farma aur madad kar, ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": "اے دکھی لوگوں کی فریاد کو پہنچنے والے اے بے قراروں کی دعا قبول کرنے والے اور اے غم کے ماروں کی مدد کرنے والے میری سختی، تنگی، پریشانی تکلیف اور رنج و غم دور کردے جیسا کہ تو نے اپنے نبی ؐکی پریشانی دور فرمائی اور دشمن سے خوف میں ان کا مدد گار ہوا دنیا و آخرت کی پریشانیوں میں میری کفایت فرما اور مدد کر اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "YAA SAREE-KHAL MAKROOBEENA WA YAA MOJEEBA DA'WATIL MUZTARREENA WA YAA MOGHEE-SAL MAHMOOMEENA IKSHIF A'NNEE ZURREE WA HAMMEE WA KARBEE WA GHAMMEE KAMAA KA-SHAFTA A'N NABIYYEKA SALLAL LAAHO A'LAYHE WA AALEHI HAMMAHU WA KAFAYTAHU HAWLA A'DUWWEHI WAK-FENEE MAA AHAMMANEE MIN AMRID DUNYAA WAL AAKHERATE YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "يَا صَرِيْخَ الْمَكْرُوْبِيْنَ وَيَا مُجِيْبَ دَعْوَةِ الْمُضْطَرِّيْنَ وَيَا مُغِيْثَ الْمَهْمُوْ